{
  "stem": "25027.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were right behind the apartment buildings set up with our mortars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the point people went into the apartment buildings, high up, to observe the German side with their binoculars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't cross the river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had orders not to cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But some people were trying to cross from the enemy side, escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we had standing orders not to let anybody cross from the enemy's side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They shoot them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The infantry were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No matter who they were, they didn't want them for some reason.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way I see it is that they had the Polish-- after they eliminated all the Jews, the Polish underground-- who was also responsible for some of that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they called themselves Armia Krajowa, the People's Army.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] started the fight against the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Russians didn't want to interfere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted that army exterminated by the Germans [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because they were planning ahead to take the country over, you know, to-- so Poland would become a communist country.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So as many Poles from this underground Polish army that died, that was their-- this is the way I saw it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the point man with two other car-- Jeeps, like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if they were American Jeeps or what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was the second Jeep to drive in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We saw stacks of bodies [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] piled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Hundreds of bodies, frozen, [SOBBING] piled up on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
